


<div class="container p-t-md">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="panel panel-default panel-profile m-b-md">
        <div class="panel-body text-center">
          <%= link_to image_tag("oc_logo_200px.png", 
                                :alt => "Over Coffee with Rev. Dave Thompson",
                                :class => "panel-profile-img",
                                :style => "-ms-transform: rotate(7deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(7deg); transform: rotate(7deg);"),
              root_path %>

          <h5 class="panel-title">
            Welcome<br>
          </h5>

          <p class="m-b-md">Over Coffee is a (roughly) 30-minute weekly Sunday morning web series where Rev. Dave Thompson listens to the <strong>spiritual stories of everyday people</strong>.</p>

          <%= link_to button_tag("About the Show", :type => "button", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), :controller => "about" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>


    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <ul class="list-group media-list media-list-stream">


        <li class="media list-group-item p-a">
        <%= link_to image_tag("this_sunday.png", 
                              :alt => "This Sunday 8am",
                              :class => "panel-profile-img center-block",
                              :style => "-ms-transform: rotate(-17deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(-17deg); transform: rotate(-17deg);"),
            "http://overcoffee.tv" %>
          <a class="media-left" href="#">
            <span class="icon icon-youtube"></span>
          </a>
          <div class="media-body">
            <div class="media-heading">
              <small class="pull-right text-muted">Sunday Jan 31, 2016</small>
              <h5>"What Would YOU Say To God?"</h5>
              <h6>Selections from Over Coffee with Rev. Dave Thompson.</h6>
            </div>

            <p><iframe width="80%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hQHU6eicD1s" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen class="center-block"></iframe></p>
            <p>
              
              <strong>Spiritual Tags</strong>
              <%= link_to button_tag("Muslim", :type => "button", :title => "Muslim", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), :controller => "home" %>
              <%= link_to button_tag("Methodist", :type => "button", :title => "Methodist", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), :controller => "home" %>
              <%= link_to button_tag("Agnostic", :title => "Agnostic", :type => "button", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), :controller => "home" %>
            </p>
            <p>
              This episode features a selection of clips from previous episodes where Rev. Dave Thompson asks his guests, "What would you ask or say to God if God were sitting with us?".
            </p>

          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>

      
      <ul class="list-group media-list media-list-stream">


        <li class="media list-group-item p-a">
        <%= link_to image_tag("last-sunday-magnet.png", 
                              :alt => "Last Sunday 8am",
                              :class => "panel-profile-img center-block",
                              :style => "-ms-transform: rotate(17deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(17deg); transform: rotate(17deg);"),
            "http://overcoffee.tv" %>
          <a class="media-left" href="#">
            <span class="icon icon-youtube"></span>
          </a>
          <div class="media-body">
            <div class="media-heading">
              <small class="pull-right text-muted">Sunday Jan 10, 2016</small>
              <h5>Marri Larson</h5>
              <h6>A Seamstress</h6>
            </div>

            <p><iframe width="80%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/65HYO8_RVt0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen class="center-block"></iframe></p>
            <p>
              
              <strong>Spiritual Tags</strong>
              <%= link_to button_tag("Christian", :type => "button", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), :controller => "home" %>
              <%= link_to button_tag("Catholic", :type => "button", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), :controller => "home" %>
            </p>
            <p>
              Merri shares about her early Christian experience and talks about her early life in Minnesota and her journey of faith to northern California. Chloé Wallace shares an original piece performed at a coffee shop in Tacoma, WA.
            </p>

          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      
      <ul class="list-group media-list media-list-stream">

        <li class="media list-group-item p-a">
          <%= link_to image_tag("previous-episodes-magnet.png", 
                                :alt => "Previous Episodes",
                                :class => "panel-profile-img center-block",
                              :style => "-ms-transform: rotate(-4deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(-4deg); transform: rotate(-4deg);"),
              "http://www.youtube.com/c/OvercoffeeTv", :target => "_blank" %>
          <div class="media-body">
            <div class="media-heading text-center">

              <p><strong>For more episodes, visit our</strong></p>
              <p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/c/OvercoffeeTv" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-youtube"></span> YouTube Channel (OverCoffeeTv)</a></p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </li>

      </ul>
      
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">

      <div class="panel panel-default panel-profile m-b-md">
        <div class="panel-body text-center">
          <%= link_to image_tag("dave_circle_headpic.jpg", 
                                  :alt => "Over Coffee with Rev. Dave Thompson", 
                                  :style => "-ms-transform: rotate(1deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(1deg); transform: rotate(1deg);",
                                  :class => "panel-profile-img center-block"),
                                "http://about.me/revdavethompson",
                                :target => "_blank" %>

          <h5 class="panel-title">
            <a class="text-inherit" href="profile/index.html">Rev. Dave Thompson</a>
          </h5>

          <ul class="list-unstyled list-spaced text-center">
              <li><span class="text-muted icon icon-calendar"></span> Make an <a href="https://www.calendly.com/revdave" target="_blank" title="Rev Dave's Calendar">Appointment</a></li>
              <li><span class="text-muted icon icon-facebook"></span> Connect on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/davethompsonpage" target="_blank" title="Rev Dave's Facebook">Facebook</a></li>
              <li><span class="text-muted icon icon-twitter"></span> Connect on <a href="http://twitter.com/revdavethompson" target="_blank" title="Rev Dave's Twitter">Twitter</a></li>
              <li><span class="text-muted icon icon-google-play"></span> Songs on <a href="https://play.google.com/store/music/album/D_a_Thompson_Disclaimer?id=Bkjlgjpday6f4k5cu6sehs6pkye" target="_blank" title="Rev Dave's Music">iTunes</a></li>
              <li><span class="text-muted icon icon-book"></span> Books on <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Over-Coffee-Conversation-Partnership-Conservative/dp/0983567735/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1441824909&sr=8-1&keywords=over+coffee" target="_blank" title="Rev Dave's Books on Amazon">Amazon</a></li>
              <li><span class="text-muted icon icon-github"></span> Software on <a href="https://github.com/worlduniting/" target="_blank" title="Rev Dave's Github">Github</a></li>
          </ul>

          <%= link_to button_tag("About.me", :type => "button", :class => "btn btn-primary-outline btn-sm"), "http://about.me/revdavethompson", :target => "_blank" %>
        </div>

      </div>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>

      <div class="panel panel-default panel-link-list">
      <%= link_to image_tag("world-uniting-magnet.png", 
                              :alt => "World Uniting, Intl'", 
                              :style => "-ms-transform: rotate(-7deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(-7deg); transform: rotate(-7deg);",
                              :class => "panel-profile-img center-block"),
                            "http://worlduniting.org",
                            :target => "_blank" %>
        <div class="panel-body">
          
          © 2015 <a href="http://worlduniting.org" target="_blank">World Uniting, Intl'</a>

          <p>World Uniting’s mission is to promote peace by providing programs that facilitate empathy in order to learn how to love others whose world views may fundamentally conflict with our own.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

